### Integration Guidelines

- Use Browserbase for browser automation within CrewAI agents
- Follow StepResult pattern for all browser operations
- Implement tenant-aware session management
- Handle errors gracefully with retry logic
- Respect rate limits and resource constraints

### Environment Setup

```bash
BROWSERBASE_API_KEY=your-browserbase-api-key
BROWSERBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-browserbase-project-id
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
OPENAI_MODEL_NAME=gpt-4-turbo
```

### Agent Integration

- Create browser tools that inherit from [BaseTool](mdc:src/ultimate_discord_intelligence_bot/tools/_base.py)
- Return StepResult with browser operation outcomes
- Include session management and cleanup
- Log browser actions for debugging and monitoring
